# Deploy (ridelogger-site)

Isti sadržaj u repou: **`docs/DEPLOY_PRODUCTION.md`**.

## Kratak tok

1. Build u Dockeru: `docker exec -e PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://app.servisna-knjizica.com sk-site sh -c 'cd /app && npm run build'`
2. Rsync `dist/` na server: `root@159.89.22.200:/var/www/ridelogger-site/`
3. `chown -R www-data:www-data /var/www/ridelogger-site`
4. Apache `DocumentRoot` za `www.servisna-knjizica.com`: `/var/www/ridelogger-site` (HTTP + HTTPS vhostovi u `sites-available/servisna-knjizica.com*.conf`)

Posle izmene vhosta: `apache2ctl configtest && systemctl reload apache2`.
